W. E. Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/W._E._Lawrence 0 William Effingham Lawrence (August 22, 1896 – November 28, 1947) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 120 films between 1912 and 1947. He was born in Brooklyn, New York and died in Hollywood, California.
